    <data key="d0">T-Mobile GitOps Managed Kubernetes Platform</data>
    <data key="d1">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1ZLiRT0C2Yo</data>
    <data key="d2">Standardized Kubernetes infrastructure deployed via GitOps and Terraform across regions and local zones, featuring high availability and hybrid connectivity.</data>
